{"word":"νικάω","slug":"νικάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νιϰάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νίκη\">νίκη</a></el>] ‘win victory (over)’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b>overcome, defeat <a href='B:490 11:22'>Lk 11:22</a>; <a href='B:500 16:33'>J 16:33</a>; <a href='B:690 2:13'>1 J 2:13</a>; <a href='B:730 11:7'>Rv 11:7</a>; <a href='B:730 12:11'>12:11</a>; <a href='B:730 13:7'>13:7</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μὴ\">μὴ</a> νιϰῶ ὑπὸ τοῦ ϰαϰοῦ, ἀλλὰ νίϰα <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> τῷ ἀγαϑῷ τὸ ϰαϰόν</el> don’t permit yourself to be overcome by evil (= don’t succumb to evil) but overcome evil by good <b><a href='B:520 12:21'>Ro 12:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ abs.\">abs.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>overcome <a href='B:520 3:4'>Ro 3:4</a></b> (of winning a legal case); <b><a href='B:730 2:7'>Rv 2:7</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Νικάνωρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:νίκη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}